@startuml
title Activity Diagram - Place Hold
skinparam style strictuml

/' TEXT DESCRIPTION (Steps)
1. Member selects a book and requests a hold.
2. System checks member status.
3. System checks hold limit policy.
4. If allowed, system creates a reservation.
5. System confirms hold placement and queue position.
6. When a copy becomes available, system sends notification.
'/

start
:Select Book and request hold;
:Check member status;

if (Member active?) then (Yes)
  :Check hold limit policy;
  if (Within limit?) then (Yes)
    :Create Reservation;
    :Show confirmation and queue position;
    :Wait for copy availability;
    :Send hold available notification;
  else (No)
    :Show hold limit exceeded;
  endif
else (No)
  :Show account blocked or inactive;
endif

stop
@enduml